<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.5.10">
<l>koṭiyē ṟucentā maraikkai viralkaḷ</l>
<l rend="indent">kōla mumaḻin tilavā ṭiṟṟila</l>
<l>vaṭivē ṟutiru vukirnon tumila</l>
<l rend="indent">maṇivaṇ ṇaṉmalai yumōrcam piratam</l>
<l>muṭiyē ṟiyamā mukiṟpal kaṇaṅkaḷ</l>
<l rend="indent">muṉṉeṟ ṟinarait taṉapō leṅkum</l>
<l>kuṭiyē ṟiyirun tumaḻai poḻiyum</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvart taṉameṉ ṉuṅkoṟṟak kuṭaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain of the jewel coloured one,</l>
<l rend="indent">The beauty of the fingers of [his] red lotus hands,</l>
<l rend="indent">spreading [like] a creeper did not fail or faulter;</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] the divine finger nails, [their] beauty growing,</l>
<l rend="indent">were not damaged, [what] a wonder!</l>
<l>called Govardhana,</l>
<l rend="indent">where rain pours down everywhere, settling in,</l>
<l rend="indent">as many clusters of black clouds ascend the summit,</l>
<l rend="indent">[appearing] as if the front side [of the mountain] has faded,</l>
<l>is [his] victory umbrella!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
